1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:10,759
Hey, pigeon.

4
00:00:10,760 --> 00:00:12,839
Do you have any travel money on you?

5
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:15,199
If not, I'm roasting you.

6
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:18,480
Sprinkle some cumin.
I want roast pigeon.

7
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:21,360
Princess, what amazing aim!

8
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,880
Princess!

9
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:24,880
Princess, look.

10
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:27,999
These are the new guards and maids
who just joined the manor.

11
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,119
From today onward,

12
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,399
we're one big family now.

13
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:33,799
And they all brought gifts for you.

14
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:34,919
Watch this.

15
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:37,719
Come on, dear family members.

16
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:40,719
Let's shout the slogan
we practiced earlier one more time, alright?

17
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:41,719
Alright!

18
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:43,479
Raise your hands.

19
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:45,959
Ready, begin!

20
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,999
The Princess is the earth!
The Princess is the heavens!

21
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:50,480
The Princess
is three quarters of our lives!

22
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:54,539
Where did Shiwan even come up with

23
00:00:54,540 --> 00:00:55,840
such a cringey slogan?

24
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:58,040
I did.

25
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:01,239
No wonder it's so poetic.

26
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,839
I should go learn from him too.

27
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,040
Being a daughter
obsessed father is terrifying.

28
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:07,680
What's this thing?

29
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,240
Time to roast pigeon!

30
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,359
Roast pigeon!

31
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:17,039
Now that's a dish I'm good at.

32
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,279
Princess, I'll teach you.

33
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,599
Alright, dismissed, everyone.

34
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,040
Princess, wait for me.

35
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,480
Your Highness.

36
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:30,860
(Imperial Preceptor, deal
with Xiao Suisui as soon as possible)

37
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:34,240
This looks like
Consort Shu's handwriting.

38
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,520
All these years,

39
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,440
she has always favored Xiao Jing.

40
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,400
I've long grown used to it.

41
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,080
But now,

42
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:49,960
she's set her sights on my daughter.

43
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,840
She may not protect her child,

44
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,360
but I

45
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,080
certainly will.

46
00:01:58,220 --> 00:02:00,460
(Imperial Preceptor Manor)

47
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:11,580
(Wu Wang, Imperial Preceptor
of Tianxuan Kingdom)

48
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,300
(From Princess Xiao Suisui)
(The pigeon tasted great.)

49
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:25,560
(of Prince Jing Manor)
(Please teach me how to raise them.)

50
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,760
My...

51
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:38,280
My messenger pigeon!

52
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,240
That little brat!

53
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,320
That little brat!

54
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,119
I'm going to...

55
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:51,080
I'm going to...

56
00:02:57,720 --> 00:03:00,280
Idiot.

57
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:04,500
(Xiao)

58
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:08,240
This is my surname.

59
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,000
Practice this first.

60
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,919
Copy it carefully,

61
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:13,000
stroke by stroke. No slacking off.

62
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,319
Father, look.

63
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,919
This is your hair.

64
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,399
This is your face.

65
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,000
This is your neck.

66
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,519
I invented a new kind of writing.

67
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,959
It's called picture writing.

68
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,680
Pretty amazing, right?

69
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,679
You know what?

70
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,879
It really does look
a bit like Prince Jing.

71
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,439
Dajun.

72
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,159
Here.

73
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:45,280
Run twenty laps around the manor.

74
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,960
Thirty laps.

75
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,039
No, wait...

76
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,480
Forty.

77
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:54,160
One, two.

78
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,840
A jade pendant from Consort Shu.

79
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,320
How much could this sell for?

80
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,400
Selling it to a pawnshop
would be a waste.

81
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:08,200
Hmm. I'll keep it
and wait for it to appreciate.

82
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:13,319
An embroidered pouch, one coin.

83
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,760
Today's total earnings...

84
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,960
I made a fortune.

85
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,480
Suisui,

86
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,560
I'm teaching you how to write.

87
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,320
Why won't you learn?

88
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,320
Writing won't make money.

89
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:29,440
Knowledge and reason
are what make a person successful.

90
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,399
Father, you're wrong.

91
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:34,240
Getting rich is better
than becoming successful.

92
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,519
Once you're rich,

93
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:38,359
you can hire as many tutors as you want.

94
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,879
Then they can do the writing for me.

95
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:43,040
All I have to do is count the money.

96
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,720
You're completely obsessed with money.

97
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,400
Suisui,

98
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,799
how about I take you to
the Imperial Academy tomorrow?

99
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,759
No.

100
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,319
Teachers are so boring.

101
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,880
Then forget it.

102
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:01,719
I just heard that the students
at the Imperial Academy

103
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:04,239
are all quite generous with money.

104
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,680
What a pity.

105
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,359
Father, I'm going tomorrow.

106
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,679
I promise I'll study hard

107
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,759
and improve every day.

108
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,920
Then earn all their money.

109
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,199
Uncle Shiwan.

110
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,079
Yes?

111
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,999
Prepare a school bag for me.

112
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,959
A really big one.

113
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,399
Alright.

114
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:25,479
One that can hold
at least five hundred taels of silver.

115
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,440
No problem!

116
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:31,079
Isn't Uncle Shiwan hard of hearing?

117
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,459
How did he hear that?

118
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:39,780
(Imperial Academy)

119
00:05:41,570 --> 00:05:42,200
Let's go.

120
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,280
Hello, everyone.

121
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,600
(Xiao Rui, Xiao Jing's son)
Please take care of me.

122
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,880
(and the eldest imperial grandson)
You're just a picked up wild girl.

123
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,400
What makes you think
you're worthy of studying with us?

124
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:59,019
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

125
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:02,859
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

126
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:06,379
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

127
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:09,340
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

128
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:13,859
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

129
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:17,620
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

130
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:21,019
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

131
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:25,060
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

132
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:34,339
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

133
00:06:34,340 --> 00:06:37,979
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

134
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:41,699
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

135
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:45,339
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

136
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:49,019
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

137
00:06:49,020 --> 00:06:50,939
♪Endlessly flowing♪

138
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:57,140
♪Good fortune♪
